Entry.JapaneseText: この地下道を抜ければお城なんだよネ。
Entry.EnglishText: If we go through this passage, we'll make it to the castle, right?
Entry.Notes: maybe not most literal but this skit is a ho

Entry.JapaneseText: 俺もここの事は初めて知ったが、 この通路が王城の方角に向かっているのは確かだ。
Entry.EnglishText: While I was unaware of it, I can say for certain that it indeed leads to the castle.
